{"tid":967094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 又贏！深圳TCL硏發的天氣App被指在用戶不知情下訂購付費服務","createTime":"2019-01-03T09:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T09:44:22.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"88a113bb98ec19fc91b39458d425af4d7d42f5fc","tid":967094,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:05:55.000Z","msg":"Now新聞台】有深圳企業研發的天氣預報手機應用程式，被指秘密收集用戶數據，並企圖在用戶不知情下訂購付費服務。<br />\n<br />\n涉事中國企業是位於深圳的TCL通訊科技控股有限公司。<br />\n<br />\n美國《華爾街日報》報道，倫敦商務安全公司「上游系統」研究發現，TCL在中國的伺服器會通過它建立的這個天氣預報免費手機應用程式，收集大量用戶數據，除用戶位置外，還收集電郵地址和每個手機專屬的國際行動裝置識別碼，應用程式還企圖暗中為TCL生產的低成本阿爾卡特智能手機的用戶，訂購虛擬實境服務。<br />\n<br />\n受影響用戶超過十萬人，他們來自巴西、馬來西亞和尼日利亞等國家，如果沒有阻截訂購，用戶會被收取總共超過150萬美元的款項。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=332863\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D332863&d=0uxXn7C%2FpHl%2FswxxB4gUX8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=f03ba7b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D332863&h=9bd1536c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=332863</a>"},{"pid":"5a323728afda4ccab84332beb5201cbc19912696","tid":967094,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:06:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb79b36c96939f54014bbb2619902c41fb0d016","tid":967094,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"老貓U裝咗V7 pay同支那寶香港，die soon <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0792efa3155174c80a2270c5e6548d625820b94","tid":967094,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeb79b36c96939f54014bbb2619902c41fb0d016","tid":967094,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"老貓U裝咗V7 pay同支那寶香